View.Description: Insert labor not saving on webclient

ConfigurationOption.Value: select l.laborcode, l.transtype, l.craft, l.startdate, l.starttime, l.finishdate, l.finishtime, l.regularhrs, l.genapprservreceipt, l.premiumpaycode, l.premiumpayhours, wo.workorderid, l.orgid, l.labtransid from labtrans l join workorder wo on l.refwo = wo.wonum and l.siteid = wo.siteid

Struct._value: := test( ${Finish Time} is null, ${Finish Date}, CreateDate( GetDateTimePart( ${Finish Date}, 'year' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Finish Date}, 'month' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Finish Date}, 'day' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Finish Time}, 'hour' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Finish Time}, 'minute' ) ) )

:= test( ${Start Time} is null, ${Start Date}, CreateDate( GetDateTimePart( ${Start Date}, 'year' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Start Date}, 'month' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Start Date}, 'day' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Start Time}, 'hour' ), GetDateTimePart( ${Start Time}, 'minute' ) ) )

EventAction.Condition: ${Finish Time} is null and ${Start Time} is not null
${Finish Time} is not null and ${Start Time} is null
${Finish Time} is null and ${Start Time} is null
${Start Date} is null and ${Finish Date} is not null
${Start Time} is not null and ${Finish Time} is not null and ${Regular Hours} is null
${Finish Date} is null and ${Start Date} is not null
${Start Time} is not null and ${Finish Time} is not null and ${CALC_FINISH} < ${CALC_START}

ConfigurationOption.Value: Finish Time (${Finish Time}) can not be before Start Time (${Start Time})!

EventAction.Condition: ${Start Time} is not null and ${Finish Time} is not null and ${Regular Hours} is null
